Description: 
gst_video_decoder_decide_allocation_default didn't consider the
buffer being a DMA DRM buffer, and got the wrong vinfo.
 gst-plugins-base1.0 (1.26.2-1+rpt1) trixie; urgency=medium
 .
   * video: Add GST_VIDEO_FORMAT_NV12_128C8 for Broadcom SAND
     8bit format
   * video: Add GST_VIDEO_FORMAT_NV12_10LE32_128C8 for
     Broadcom SAND 10bit format
Author: Serge Schneider <serge@raspberrypi.com>

